msgid ""
"This unit can hide in certain terrain, and remain undetected by its "
"enemies.\n"
"\n"
"Enemy units cannot see this unit while it is hiding in certain terrain, "
"except if they have units next to it. The player is able to select which "
"terrain class to target with this ability by right-clicking the unit before "
"it moves or engages in combat on any turn, as long as it is not adjacent to "
"an enemy unit.\n"
"\n"
"Any enemy unit that first discovers this unit immediately loses all its "
"remaining movement."
